  "2026-02-23T18:06:11.005Z",cursor-maintainer,"Planned change-set: audit RFC6902 patch generation determinism and strengthen unit coverage for canonical before/after patch output; update tracking links and close this task with evidence if criteria are met."
  "2026-02-23T18:07:11.136Z",cursor-maintainer,"Implemented deterministic patch-assertion coverage in tests/unit/determinism.spec.ts: asserts exact RFC6902 operations and verifies identical patch/hash output when front-matter keys are reordered."
  "2026-02-23T18:19:37.923Z",cursor-maintainer,"Evidence: updated tests/unit/determinism.spec.ts to assert exact RFC6902 replace operations and key-order invariant patch/hash output. Verification passed via pm test pm-p9z --run --timeout 2400 --json (2/2 linked tests passed, including node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage and targeted determinism spec). Regression sweeps passed: pm test-all --status in_progress --timeout 2400 --json -> items=9 linked_tests=32 passed=14 failed=0 skipped=18; pm test-all --status closed --timeout 2400 --json -> items=31 linked_tests=111 passed=48 failed=0 skipped=63. Coverage remained 100% lines/branches/functions/statements."
  "2026-04-03T11:55:43.049Z",codex-agent,"Mapped external-audit Issue 8: add user-facing item diff/verify capability leveraging deterministic history patch data."
  "2026-04-03T11:59:28.390Z",codex-agent,"Wave3 scope: diff/verify surfaces are additive and must not alter existing history/activity payload contracts."
  "2026-04-03T13:25:06.010Z",codex-agent,"Implementation pass started: delivering additive scope from approved plan, with targeted tests and full verification before close."
  "2026-04-03T14:12:28.677Z",codex-agent,"Delivered additive history diagnostics with pm history --diff and --verify, including main wiring, contract metadata, Pi mapping, and targeted history command tests. Evidence: pm test pm-p9z --run --json passed all three linked commands including coverage and determinism plus integration regression."
